# Metadata Database Implementation Status Document

**Date:** 15 May 2026

---

# 1. Purpose

This document records the current implementation status of the PostgreSQL metadata database for the Database Schema and Data Migration Platform.

As of the above date, the database has been successfully implemented and verified on the local development environment.

This document serves as:

* Database implementation reference
* Local setup tracking document
* Future hosted database migration reference
* Schema recreation guide
* Persistence architecture status document

The current implementation exists in a local PostgreSQL database instance and is planned to be migrated later to a hosted/cloud-managed PostgreSQL deployment.

