# 8. Trigger Function Implemented

The following trigger function has been implemented for automatic timestamp updates.

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION migration.update_updated_at_column()
RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$
BEGIN
    NEW.updated_at = NOW();
    RETURN NEW;
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;
```

---

# 9. Trigger Implemented

```sql
CREATE TRIGGER update_jobs_updated_at
BEFORE UPDATE
ON migration.migration_jobs
FOR EACH ROW
EXECUTE FUNCTION migration.update_updated_at_column();
```

